{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "tiphub-price-data-v1",
    "name": "Tiphub Price Data API",
    "description": "# Tiphub Developer API\n\nComplete API collection for the Tiphub financial market analysis platform.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n1. **Set base URL**: Update the `base_url` collection variable (default: `https://tiphub.ai`)\n2. **Create an account**: Run the **Signup** or **Login** request — JWT tokens auto-save to collection variables\n3. **Create an API key**: Run **Developer > Create API Key** — the key auto-saves to `api_key`\n4. **Start exploring**: Most market data endpoints work with just the API key\n\n## Authentication\n\n| Method | Header | Used For |\n|--------|--------|----------|\n| **JWT Bearer** | `Authorization: Bearer <token>` | Web app endpoints (auth, subscription, admin, developer, saved results) |\n| **API Key** | `X-API-Key: <key>` | Data API endpoints (market data, prices, screener, backtest, sentiment) |\n| **None** | — | Public endpoints (health checks, config, subscription plans) |\n\n## Rate Limits\n\n| Tier | Requests/min | Screener/day | Backtest/day |\n|------|-------------|--------------|--------------|\n| Basic (Free) | 30 | 3 | 3 |\n| Premium | 120 | Unlimited | Unlimited |\n\n## Error Codes\n\n| Code | Meaning |\n|------|---------|\n| 400 | Bad Request — invalid parameters |\n| 401 | Unauthorized — missing or invalid token/key |\n| 403 | Forbidden — insufficient tier or permissions |\n| 404 | Not Found — resource doesn't exist |\n| 409 | Conflict — duplicate resource |\n| 429 | Too Many Requests — rate limit exceeded |\n| 500 | Internal Server Error |\n\n## SSE Streaming Endpoints\n\nScreener, Backtest, Sentiment, and Chat endpoints use Server-Sent Events (SSE) for real-time progress.\nUse the **Start** endpoint to get a task/job ID, then connect to the **Stream** endpoint.\nPostman shows raw SSE text; for best results test SSE in browser or with `curl`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://tiphub.ai",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "jwt_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_key",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "test_ticker",
      "value": "RELIANCE",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "test_task_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "noauth"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          ""
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Price Data",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Stock LTP (Single)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "X-API-Key",
                "value": "{{api_key}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/stock-ltp/{{test_ticker}}",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "stock-ltp",
                "{{test_ticker}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Real-time Last Traded Price with intraday OHLC for a single stock.\n\n**Auth:** API Key (optional)\n**Cache:** 1 minute\n**Source:** `ltp_live` table (cleared EOD)"
